                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for continuously synthesizing lithium hexafluorophosphate",
                    "一种连续合成六氟磷酸锂的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for continuously synthesizing lithium hexafluorophosphate, which comprises the following steps: (1) adding lithium fluoride into a reaction kettle containing anhydrous hydrofluoric acid for reaction to obtain an anhydrous hydrofluoric acid solution of lithium hydrogen fluoride; (2) continuously introducing a mixed gas of PF5 and HCl into the anhydrous hydrofluoric acid solution of lithium hydrogen fluoride, reacting to obtain an anhydrous hydrofluoric acid solution of LiPF6, and discharging the unreacted HCl gas into a tail gas absorption system after passing through a condenser; (3) along with continuous introduction of the mixed gas of PF5 and HCl, supplementing lithium fluoride into the reaction kettle, continuously separating out the LiPF6 after the concentration of the LiPF6 in the solution is saturated, and settling the LiPF6 in a filtering device; and (4) carrying out solid-liquid separation on the precipitated LiPF6 crystal, and drying to obtain a lithium hexafluorophosphate product. According to the method, a traditional cooling crystallization process is not needed, the energy consumption is reduced, the crystallization efficiency is improved, and the prepared lithium hexafluorophosphate product is good in quality and can be directly used in the lithium ion battery electrolyte."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种连续合成六氟磷酸锂的方法，包括以下步骤：(1)将氟化锂加入到含有无水氢氟酸的反应釜中反应，获得氟化氢锂的无水氢氟酸溶液；(2)将PF5和HCl混合气连续通入氟化氢锂的无水氢氟酸溶液中，反应获得LiPF6的无水氢氟酸溶液，未反应的HCl气体经冷凝器后排出至尾气吸收系统；(3)随着PF5和HCl混合气的连续通入，向反应釜中补加氟化锂，溶液中LiPF6浓度达到饱和后连续析出，并沉降至过滤装置；(4)析出的LiPF6晶体固液分离、干燥即得到六氟磷酸锂产品。本发明无需采用传统的降温结晶工艺，不仅降低能耗、提高结晶效率，且制备的六氟磷酸锂产品质量好，可直接用于锂离子电池电解液中。"
                }
            ]
